CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 2, 1959, pg. A12 reads: "Iotas Honor Nancy Lee - Iota Phi Lambda sorors cited Nancy Lee of Juvenile Court, and fellow member, Soror Ann L. Penn, of Kay Club, at the sorority's spring luncheon and hat show. Left to right: President Katie E. Johnson, Jean S. Farrish, chairman; Sorors Lee and Penn, honorees; Lois Lee Dorsey, making the presentation to Miss Lee, and Shirley Reizenbecker of Arlee Hats. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Iota Phi Lambda members, from left: Katie E. Johnson, Jean S. Farrish, Nancy Lee and Ann L. Penn, honorees; Lois Lee Dorsey, and Shirley Reizenbecker, standing in interior with light colored walls and large wall sconce during spring luncheon and hat show
